          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-9533 test: update how to get version in obdfilter-survey",
        "message": "LU-9533 test: update how to get version in obdfilter-survey\n\nThe routine get_lustre_version() in lustre-iokit/obdfilter-survey\nexpects the string \"lustre\" in the return value of 'lctl get_param\n-n version'. Unfortunately, \"lustre\" is no longer returned as part\nof the version string.\n\nRemove the code looking for the string \"lustre\" from the\nreturn value of 'lctl get_param -n version'.\n\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ifbeed05952d5fdb1333544bfcda90acfc0cefa8a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
